{"id": 6457, "title": "Ticket #6457: Milestone 4 for late materialization", "description": "<blockquote>\nEnhancements to late materialization for 8.7.5\n\n<p></p><ol>\n<li>don't require a submit command line argument for late materialization\n\n<p></p></li><li>report materialize failures in the user log. (and the cluster object?)\n\n<p></p></li><li>add more flexible policy for controlling whether jobs materialize or not.\n\n<p></p></li><li>Make it possible to pause/resume the factory using a tool. Currently condor_hold &lt;cluster_id&gt; will pause the factory also, but there should probably be a way to pause the factory without also holding all of the materialized jobs.\n\n<p></p></li><li>Load foreach data into memory only when needed, don't keep it around after we are done with it.</li></ol>\n</blockquote>", "remarks": "<blockquote>\n<em>2017-Dec-13 14:40:58 by johnkn:</em> <br/>\n\nTasks 1 and 2 were completed for the 8.7.6 release. 3, 4 &amp; 5 will be punted to the future.</blockquote>", "derived_tickets": "<table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\n<tbody><tr><td align=\"right\" valign=\"top\" width=\"160\">\n<span class=\"ticket\"><a class=\"resolved\" href=\"/wiki-archive/tickets/?ticket=6471\" onclick=\"get_ticket_and_populate_wrapper('6471'); return false;\" title=\"use max_materialize in submit to enable late materialization\">#6471</a></span></td>\n<td align=\"center\" valign=\"center\" width=\"30\">\n<span class=\"icon ptr1\">\u00a0</span></td>\n<td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\">\nuse max_materialize in submit to enable late materialization</td></tr>\n<tr><td align=\"right\" valign=\"top\" width=\"160\">\n<span class=\"ticket\"><a class=\"resolved\" href=\"/wiki-archive/tickets/?ticket=6475\" onclick=\"get_ticket_and_populate_wrapper('6475'); return false;\" title=\"preen erroneously removes submit digests for active clusters\">#6475</a></span></td>\n<td align=\"center\" valign=\"center\" width=\"30\">\n<span class=\"icon ptr1\">\u00a0</